name: AlgoStake
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Algorand ASA Staking 

Set up staking for customers who hold your coin and incentivize them to hold your Algorand ASA over the long term. Staking/ liquid farming app for the Algorand blockchain. High yields/ APRS available for multiple assets.
